FBIS4-25413 "drchi112_f_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-112 Daily Report 5 Jun 1994 Near East & South Asia One Chinese, Two Iranians Kidnapped in South Iran One Chinese, Two Iranians Kidnapped in South Iran OW0506130594 Beijing XINHUA in English 1234 GMT 5 Jun 94 OW0506130594 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Tehran, June 5 (XINHUA) -- One Chinese and two Iranians were kidnapped by unidentified gunmen in southern Iran Friday [3 June], according to Iranian authorities here today. Fu Weixian, a Chinese specialist working for a mineral factory, was abducted by armed men along with his driver and another Iranian accompanying him.
